          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.Two main gamma-lines from the EC decay of",
                " 239Cm were observed at 188.2 and 146.2 keV, with",
                "absolute abundances of 36% and 12%, respectively, from",
                "the decay of daughter 239Am. The alpha-branch of 239Cm",
                "was determined to have an upper limit of less than",
                " 1*10E-5."
              ]
            }
          ],
