                    "date": 1992
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " In absolute numbers, all measured cross sections are",
                "approximately a factor of 20 below the values",
                "calculated with HIVAP(see REL-REF). This discrepancy is",
                "not understood. However, the low cross sections",
                "measured in this work do not appear to be out of line",
                "with other reported results."
              ]
            }
